data.description: Welcome to 534 Westbend, San Antonio - a solid home with a solid foundation! The HVAC system, just over a year old, ensures modern comfort. Recently updated kitchen and bathroom. This property presents a fantastic investment opportunity, with little left to be done. Make it yours today and enjoy the convenience of being just 11 minutes from Lackland AFB and a short 7-minute drive to various restaurants and shops. Don't miss out on this promising investment!
